{"tid":2059024,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人都發覺 原來一年前既自己係幾咁幼稚","createTime":"2020-06-10T14:51:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-11T01:23:32.000Z","uid":61886,"like":38,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"c1476631176dd39784e24ebeb03c3d3d489d8f48","tid":2059024,"uid":61886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T14:51:33.000Z","msg":"03年50萬人遊行過令23條收皮<br />\n12年去過好多日反國教令國教暫時收皮<br />\n以為人數真係可以震撼到政權<br />\n以為6月100萬 200萬遊行會令政府退讓<br />\n<br />\n以為林鄭做到咁閪<br />\n中共會換特首<br />\n<br />\n以為之前有朱經緯/七狗案<br />\n點都會搵幾隻出位狗祭旗安撫香港人<br />\n<br />\n點知中共原來係咁撚癲<br />\n<br />\n而家諗返起 其實一年前都太睇少左中共<br />\n<br />\n不過 香港人進化得遲 但都最少進化緊<br />\n大家繼續加油啦<br />\n<br />\nPS 無聊9up下"},{"pid":"6de5e9419e923b820fb5e7ec31f8b069da8b6b92","tid":2059024,"uid":61886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T00:37:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2aac0c93569f29ae7152322d2f3b8fdb195c0167","tid":2059024,"uid":95059,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T00:38:41.000Z","msg":"唔係撒回左咩？"},{"pid":"6c40754f8f64ec44259fa96b44b7fed8a1ea6883","tid":2059024,"uid":214090,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T00:39:22.000Z","msg":"一早知遊行冇用"},{"pid":"5c45c6e6c5251c5089859ccd0f1c98ef0e06813a","tid":2059024,"uid":18615,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T00:45:03.000Z","msg":"唔行出黎既話，<br />\n外國人唔會睇到個畫面原來咁震撼"},{"pid":"b4f14ef1e6b56afafe1cbb305b593287847d788b","tid":2059024,"uid":125079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T00:47:09.000Z","msg":"習近平同林鄭條仆街"},{"pid":"5d9339a22063175dbca5cb466bd9909c30f7f183","tid":2059024,"uid":228995,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T00:55:48.000Z","msg":"你唔做，點迫國際出手"},{"pid":"70f4fee98fd5b35190f7a3bdcc01090a60e323d1","tid":2059024,"uid":121197,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T01:15:11.000Z","msg":"其實一年